{# Task List Template — renders gate-task-list.sh compliant markdown.
   Gate checks:
   TL1: Has task items (checkboxes ^\s*-\s*\[ or numbered \d+\.)
   TL2: References phases or milestones
   TL3: File size > 200 chars
#}
# Task List: {{ feature_name }}

- **Date**: {{ date }}
- **Author**: super-dev:spec-writer
- **Specification**: ./{{ spec_filename }}
- **Implementation Plan**: ./{{ plan_filename }}
- **Total Tasks**: {{ total_task_count }}

---
{% for phase in phases %}

## Phase {{ phase.number }}: {{ phase.name }}

**Milestone**: {{ phase.milestone }}
{% for task in phase.tasks %}
- [ ] **{{ task.id }}**: {{ task.description }}
  - Files: {{ task.files | join(", ") }}
  - Type: {{ task.type }}
  - Effort: {{ task.effort }}
{% if task.depends_on %}  - Depends on: {{ task.depends_on | join(", ") }}{% endif %}

{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}

---

## Summary

| Phase | Tasks | Effort |
|-------|-------|--------|
{% for phase in phases %}
| Phase {{ phase.number }}: {{ phase.name }} | {{ phase.tasks | length }} | {{ phase.effort }} |
{% endfor %}
| **Total** | {{ total_task_count }} | {{ total_effort }} |
